{"tid":625582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來朱克伯格得米七高","createTime":"2018-04-11T14:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T00:24:21.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"99570ad122866a81f3ff29e4460217c3350fa17d","tid":625582,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"Fb聽證會：朱克伯格5呎7　靠坐厚墊裝腔作勢？<br />\n04月11日(三) 15:43<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/photo/bknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_01p.jpg?20180411180440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180411180440&h=72509775&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n坐墊有一定厚度，令朱克伯格坐上後高一點。（法新社圖片）<br />\n<br />\nFacebook（Fb）始創人朱克伯格周二（10日）出席聽證會，吸引大批傳媒訪問，個子不高大的他還被發現座位上有一個4吋厚坐墊，搶走不少風頭。<br />\n<br />\n有眼利的記者發現朱克伯格坐在幾吋厚的坐墊上作供，好讓他看起來高一點。由於坐墊與坐椅同為黑色，若非細心留意，恐怕難以發現。身高5呎7吋高的朱克伯格在美國人中，身材不算高大，在聽證會遭議員轟炸，難怪要「裝腔作勢」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/photo/bknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_02p.jpg?20180411180440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_02p.jpg%3F20180411180440&h=2a4e3e5d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/photo/bknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_04p.jpg?20180411180440\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001_04p.jpg%3F20180411180440&h=9a736c0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n朱克伯格的身材，在美國人中不算高大。（美聯社圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/bknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180411%2Fbknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001.html&d=MXqbSAbZDu%2FemF4bcT8PWU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=066f8c9e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20180411/bknint-20180411154302182-0411_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bacf1c23457a05b011baf5d4f7c32c5d5e59fc03","tid":625582,"uid":43575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:43:41.000Z","msg":"White traxh"},{"pid":"80cc7b7efe681a380ef4a58ec61736975c9cda54","tid":625582,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"聽證會張椅邊個準備?"},{"pid":"99959152bc1b9a7ac0464276b8284123470ab9b1","tid":625582,"uid":43575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:47:19.000Z","msg":"朱生影衰美國人"},{"pid":"59c380068f528b7aad5e7322a1797362332e1a44","tid":625582,"uid":35014,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:48:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fff48c2139d304d8e26f15ed0a64bc14d8352fb7","tid":625582,"uid":60668,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"普京都係得米七 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bca055cd3debf8827803942b4643441a07b133f","tid":625582,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T14:50:04.000Z","msg":"PR 勁撚貼心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876e772851614fc6fac773257c670bd665323805","tid":625582,"uid":7375,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3daf7ece8ef32047cffce2641506fd37e6c61af0","tid":625582,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T17:51:50.000Z","msg":"以佢咁嘅高度舐共啱晒啦。"},{"pid":"9503289bac4c05be947fb81f3dee1c123dbd1a21","tid":625582,"uid":138762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-11T18:16:23.000Z","msg":"佢都可以攞殘津<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"